Package int3.team2.website.pantry_loogr.domain

Class Product

java.lang.Object
int3.team2.website.pantry_loogr.domain.Ingredient
int3.team2.website.pantry_loogr.domain.Product
Direct Known Subclasses:
PantryZoneProduct
public class Product extends Ingredient
Product is an extension of Ingredient, instead of just containing the broad information about a product, it also holds how much of that product is in one pack and what barCode it is associated to

      public Product(String name, String productName, String code, int size)
      Constructor to create a new Product before it is inserted into the database.

      name - the name of the ingredient
      productName - the name of the product (is often different from the ingredient it extends)
      code - the barcode associated with the product
      size - teh quantity of the product in one pack
